definitions.definition: A method of making an image by placing a piece of paper against an object and then rubbing over it, usually with a pencil or charcoal .
An illustration made by means of frottage.
The practice of rubbing parts of the body against those of another person for sexual stimulation .

main_definition: ( uncountable , art ) A method of making an image by placing a piece of paper against an object and then rubbing over it, usually with a pencil or charcoal .
secondary_definitions: ( countable , art ) An illustration made by means of frottage.
( uncountable , sexuality ) The practice of rubbing parts of the body against those of another person for sexual stimulation .
